{"tid":1284993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線新聞聲明: 保留向撐警集會與會人士的粗暴行為一切追究權利","createTime":"2019-07-04T11:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:41:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"19ca9d435d57b7e4da7c975f695cf8d3a0919b88","tid":1284993,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"本台兩名記者及一名攝影師於6月30日，在金鐘添馬公園撐警集會現場進行採訪，當時有與會人士正接受本台訪問，點評兩張記者手持的網上文宣。正當訪問進行之際，附近一批人士上前干擾採訪，拿走單張，一度推撞本台同事並粗言相向。記者出示記者證後嘗試離開，但在場人士繼續糾纏，有人拍打本台攝影機，最終記者在現場警務人員協助下離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n本台對上述事件表示遺憾，對干擾記者採訪的行為，以及近日並無事實根據的指控，本台將保留一切追究權利。"},{"pid":"94bedfd25beb8e8edebf516d3b265782c6bd0a21","tid":1284993,"uid":233039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6c47e09a5269f07e6436f2da78f1712ad1fc1cd7","tid":1284993,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdf85a452cba30e28e77f57aca02fc883ae47ce","tid":1284993,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17dee3bf55c8a373dc29011a37d811e6b05ec72","tid":1284993,"uid":211851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"睇得出撐藍絲個班人民質素係差D，成班都死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd166913c00f03f629a5213ef3f706987529369","tid":1284993,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9f5369ba6f6